snippet.title: Q-Cubed Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Q-Cubed is out now with a free demo available at https://cludosian.itch.io/q-cubed

Q-Cubed is a puzzle platformer where you navigate 3D levels while seeing the world from two orthogonal perspectives
